{"tid":580140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★24小時快餐店無家者5年內增6.7倍","createTime":"2018-03-04T08:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T10:15:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc36fca3d726e1cc287e70e7b50ccafbc30b57a","tid":580140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/164890/thumbnail/84812c282154c1cdf64e160106fcc499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F164890%2Fthumbnail%2F84812c282154c1cdf64e160106fcc499.jpg&h=c82b6d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港社區組織協會於2017年12月8日凌晨時段，即凌晨12時至早上4時，分別在四個區域中的廿四小時快餐店，包括港島、九龍東、九龍西及葵青荃，進行廿四小時快餐店無家者的人口點算。<br />\n<br />\n研究發現，過去5年「廿四小時快餐店無家者」人口，由2013年的57人增加至2017年12月的384人，增長約6.7倍，其中九龍西區（58.9%）。<br />\n<br />\n社協亦於2017年12月至2018年1月，訪問了116名廿四小時快餐店的無家者，研究對象集中於九龍西區，包括油尖旺區（55.2%）、深水埗（31%）和九龍城區（12.9%）。<br />\n<br />\n社區組織幹事吳衛東指，過去5年「全港無家者人口」增長率高37%，女性「廿四小時快餐店的無家者」較其他露宿地點為多，批目前的資助宿位不足。他稱，建議政府增加資助住宿服務宿位，尤其女性宿位，並延長宿舍住宿期至3年等，改善情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164890/24%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E5%BA%97%E7%84%A1%E5%AE%B6%E8%80%855%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E5%A2%9E6-7%E5%80%8D-%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%94%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A2%9E%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%BF%E4%BD%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F164890%2F24%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%2580%25855%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25A2%259E6-7%25E5%2580%258D-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E4%25BD%258D&d=vxBuxWVO3%2B2ha190jfl7IsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f59c6113\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164890/24%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E5%BA%97%E7%84%A1%E5%AE%B6%E8%80%855%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E5%A2%9E6-7%E5%80%8D-%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%94%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A2%9E%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%BF%E4%BD%8D</a>"},{"pid":"c2f60fddfe4a83d6a083c45ec3bcec695f0c6b06","tid":580140,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"老貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d198306eb0e4d4ca567025fdc86db5927867ff","tid":580140,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"U love sleep m記？"},{"pid":"7be564a65409409d476333b390f979713acbfb62","tid":580140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d198306eb0e4d4ca567025fdc86db5927867ff","tid":580140,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"U love sleep m記？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"MX"},{"pid":"94d89c77b797f4cca0aaf6760458bbda36d01920","tid":580140,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be564a65409409d476333b390f979713acbfb62","tid":580140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d198306eb0e4d4ca567025fdc86db5927867ff","tid":580140,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"U love sleep m記？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"MX"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:54:02.000Z","msg":"唔係好早收？"},{"pid":"43e14ec8733404023412a90998f4455d3eecb61e","tid":580140,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636d8d36a5e3ffc9ad9a985f4c5ef0215cb8e4e7","tid":580140,"uid":45460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"問題是租金太高昂, 政府服務極有限. <br />\n<br />\n有人甚至惡意批評政府不是. 我自己曾經查問過一個好嚴肅政治問題, 你可以允許少量左軚汽車使用香港路段, 是甚麼原因不允許長居香港的人登記左軚汽車使用? 你日本民法, 澳門民法甚至英國法例有寫明如何處理.我想, 是時候討論一下."}]}